    private static class BinaryResultBase.BasicBinaryResult<U>
extends BinaryResultBase<U>
    Simple override of BinaryResultBase. This holds no additional values but is used by BinaryResultBase.translate(org.apache.flink.graph.asm.translate.TranslateFunction<K, T>, org.apache.flink.graph.asm.result.TranslatableResult<T>, org.apache.flink.util.Collector<org.apache.flink.graph.asm.result.TranslatableResult<T>>) as the reuse object for translating vertex IDs.

        public java.lang.String toString()
        从类复制的说明: ResultBase
        Object.toString() must be overridden to write POJO values in the same form as Tuple. Values are comma-separated and enclosed in parenthesis, e.g. "(f0,f1)".
